7b73","importance":2,"narrative":"A reasoning hook was triggered at the specified timestamp, but no actual reasoning content or tool usage details were included in the observation. This appears to be a system-level hook capture without associated actionable information.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"System hook capture without reasoning content","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:42.505Z","title":"Reasoning hook triggered","type":"other"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tcz0i_80979ea17a7a":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM fallback chain","environment variable configuration","dual server architecture","Vercel deployment debugging","SSE streaming chat"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Chat AI returns fallback message: \"ņŻäņåĪĒĢ®ļŗłļŗż. Ēśäņ×¼ AI ņä£ļ╣äņŖżņŚÉ ņØ╝ņŗ£ņĀüņØĖ ļ¼ĖņĀ£Ļ░Ć ņ×łņŖĄļŗłļŗż.\"","call_llm() (server.py:2161-2206) fails across all LLM providers: OPENCODE, ZAI, NOUS, OPENROUTER","Fallback message trigger point: server.py:2206","LLM call sequence: OpenCode GLM-5.2 ŌåÆ ZAI GLM-5 ŌåÆ NOUS (3 models) ŌåÆ OpenRouter (2 models)","server.py uses os.environ.get() for OPENCODE_KEY (line 48), ZAI_KEY (line 35), OPENROUTER_KEY (line 44)","api/index.py (Vercel) has ZAI_KEY hardcoded at line 81","Local server runs on port 8090","Vercel deployment: stock-dashboard.vercel.app","Git repo: stock-dashboard (jmpark333/stockm main)"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","server.py","api/index.py","app.js"],"id":"obs_mr9tcz0i_80979ea17a7a","importance":7,"narrative":"Session checkpoint documents active debugging of dashboard chat AI failure. The agent has identified that call_llm() is returning the fallback message because all LLM provider chains (OpenCode, ZAI, NOUS, OpenRouter) are failing. The next step is to investigate server logs to identify the actual error messages and verify Vercel environment variable status.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Debugging failed LLM fallback chain in call_llm()","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:42.878Z","title":"Dashboard chat AI debugging session checkpoint","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tczdk_60bb8580ff26":{"observation":{"concepts":["dual server architecture","LLM fallback chain","KRX stock data integration","lightweight-charts candlestick visualization","server-side news filtering","Korean stock market time handling (KST)","Vercel serverless Flask deployment"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Project: Korean stock market dashboard (stock-dashboard) showing real-time quotes, news, AI analysis, candlestick charts for KRX stocks","Deployed on Vercel at stock-dashboard-wine-gamma.vercel.app, local dev on port 8090","LLM call order: ZAI (glm-5) ŌåÆ NOUS ŌåÆ OPENROUTER with fallback chain managed by call_llm()","Dual server architecture: server.py (local) and api/index.py (Vercel Flask) with mirrored endpoints","Frontend index display shows only change rate (%) to avoid line breaks","Chatbot uses server cache data instead of search; search is disabled","TradingView free widget does not support KRX symbols; using lightweight-charts@4.1.3 with Naver Finance siseJson.naver API","Naver Finance API returns Python list syntax (single quotes), requires ast.literal_eval()","Korean candlestick colors: up (ņ¢æļ┤ē) = red #ef5350, down (ņØīļ┤ē) = teal #26a69a","Sell fee: 0.215% (0.015% commission + 0.20% tax) deducted from sell amount"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tczdk_60bb8580ff26","importance":9,"narrative":"This file contains the durable project memory for a Korean stock market dashboard web application. It defines critical constraints including LLM provider fallback order, dual server mirroring requirements, time-zone handling (KST), and frontend display rules. The architecture decisions section explains why TradingView was rejected in favor of lightweight-charts with Naver Finance data, and documents the LLM prompt simplification strategy to reduce response latency.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Durable project-level knowledge and constraints","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:43.348Z","title":"Project memory file for stock-dashboard","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tczj9_de466ad939e6":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback","hardcoded credentials","environment variable configuration","API key management","multi-provider LLM routing"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Chat AI returned \"ņŻäņåĪĒĢ®ļŗłļŗż. Ēśäņ×¼ AI ņä£ļ╣äņŖżņŚÉ ņØ╝ņŗ£ņĀüņØĖ ļ¼ĖņĀ£Ļ░Ć ņ×łņŖĄļŗłļŗż\" for Korean stock market query","`call_llm()` fallback message triggered due to all LLM providers failing","`api/index.py` contains hardcoded ZAI_KEY","`server.py` uses environment variables for configuration","OPENCODE_KEY/OPENROUTER_KEY not set causes providers to be skipped","Root cause analysis in progress"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md","api/index.py","server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9tczj9_de466ad939e6","importance":5,"narrative":"The session notes document a turn 1 incident where the chat AI failed to respond to a Korean stock market query, triggering a fallback message. The agent is investigating why all LLM providers failed, noting configuration discrepancies between api/index.py (hardcoded ZAI_KEY) and server.py (environment variables), and identifying that missing OPENCODE_KEY/OPENROUTER_KEY environment variables cause providers to be skipped.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Troubleshooting chat AI fallback due to all LLM providers failing","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:43.552Z","title":"Session notes: LLM provider failure analysis","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tczo2_94ae3b02b795":{"observation":{"concepts":["agent lifecycle hook","step completion event"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Hook type: step_finish","Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:50:43.724Z"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9tczo2_94ae3b02b795","importance":1,"narrative":"A step_finish hook was triggered indicating completion of a processing step. No additional context or tool details were provided with this event.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Step completed at 2026-07-06T22:50:43.724Z","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:43.724Z","title":"Step finish hook triggered","type":"notification"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tczq7_528d20286db6":{"observation":{"concepts":["patch application"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:50:43.802Z","Hook value: patch_applied"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9tczq7_528d20286db6","importance":3,"narrative":"A patch was successfully applied to the system at the specified timestamp. The hook notification indicates completion of a patch operation, though no details about the patch contents or affected files are provided in this minimal event log.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Hook notification: patch_applied","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:43.802Z","title":"Patch applied at 2026-07-06T22:50:43.802Z","type":"other"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9td60c_810dbe4a190c":{"observation":{"concepts":["actor tool whitelist","tool permission enforcement","restricted execution environment"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Bash tool is not in actor's whitelist","Allowed tools: read, write, edit, apply_patch, glob, grep, task","Attempted to read /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/tasks/T1/progress.md"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/tasks/T1/progress.md"],"id":"obs_mr9td60c_810dbe4a190c","importance":5,"narrative":"An attempt to execute a bash command to read the T1 task progress file was blocked because the bash tool is not permitted for this actor. The execution environment restricts available tools to read, write, edit, apply_patch, glob, grep, and task. This prevented access to the task's progress tracking file.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Attempted to use bash to read task progress file","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:51.945Z","title":"Bash tool blocked by actor whitelist","type":"error"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9td944_f9340397a721":{"observation":{"concepts":["task management"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Task list query returned no results"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9td944_f9340397a721","importance":1,"narrative":"Queried the task management system for existing tasks; the list was empty.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Queried task system, no tasks found","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:50:55.969Z","title":"Task list empty","type":"command_run"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tddvs_640de9b62b00":{"observation":{"concepts":["glob pattern matching","file system search","progress tracking"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Pattern: **/tasks/**/progress.md","Path: /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf","Result: No files found"],"files":["N/A - no files found"],"id":"obs_mr9tddvs_640de9b62b00","importance":1,"narrative":"A glob search for progress.md files within tasks subdirectories of the session memory directory returned no matches. This indicates either the tasks directory structure doesn't exist or progress tracking files haven't been created yet.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Searched for progress.md files in tasks directories","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:51:02.141Z","title":"Progress file glob search returned no results","type":"search"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9te0ul_f5701d6c6317":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM fallback chain","API key management","dual server architecture","rate limit handling","content fallback logic","ZAI API","OpenCode API","Nous AI providers","OpenRouter API"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Dashboard chat returns \"AI service unavailable\" for all user inputs","All LLM providers in fallback chain failed: ZAI (rate limit), OpenCode (missing key), Nous (content null/404), OpenRouter (missing key)","Modified api/index.py:chat_from_nous() to use reasoning fallback when content is null, increased max_tokens 1500ŌåÆ2500","Identified duplicate OpenCode call in api/index.py lines 2372-2375 and 2407-2411","Missing env vars: OPENCODE_KEY, OPENROUTER_KEY","ZAI rate limit resets 2026-07-08 08:29:53","Nous providers: stepfun returns content=null with reasoning, two others return 404 Model not found","Dual server architecture: api/index.py (Vercel) + server.py (local) must mirror changes"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","api/index.py","server.py"],"id":"obs_mr9te0ul_f5701d6c6317","importance":8,"narrative":"Session documented failure of all LLM providers in the fallback chain for the dashboard chat. Root cause analysis revealed missing API keys, rate limits, and content=null responses. Applied code fix in api/index.py for Nous provider content fallback and identified duplicate API call and environment variable gaps.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Debugging all LLM provider failures and fixing chat_from_nous()","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:51:31.913Z","title":"Dashboard chat AI LLM debugging checkpoint","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9te8a1_69e0cd0c9d96":{"observation":{"concepts":["API rate limiting","LLM provider fallback","API response field fallback","duplicate API calls bug"],"confidence":1,"facts":["ZAI API weekly limit exhausted for key ending in LUXSKaxDozJgFHLQ, resets 2026-07-08 08:29:53","All providers failed (NOUS/OPENROUTER unconfigured) causing fallback message","Two Nous free models (gpt-oss-120b:free, nex-n2-pro:free) return 404, only stepfun works","chat_from_nous() uses reasoning field as fallback when content is null","call_llm() has duplicate OpenCode call at lines 2372-2375 and 2407-2411","Fix needed: remove duplicate call and apply reasoning fallback to server.py"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9te8a1_69e0cd0c9d96","importance":7,"narrative":"Updated project memory file with four identified issues: ZAI rate limiting causing total provider failure, two invalid Nous models needing removal, a reasoning fallback implemented only in api/index.py that needs mirroring in server.py, and a duplicate OpenCode API call bug causing guaranteed double-failure.","sessionId":"ses_0c65fd642ffeKMVzJbXbYz4wzZ","subtitle":"Added 4 new technical issues to project memory","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:51:41.540Z","title":"Update MEMORY.md with bug findings (2026-07-07)","type":"file_edit"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tei0g_9a15f6f341fc":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback","API key environment variables","multi-provider debugging"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Turn 1: Chat AI returned service fallback error on Korean stock market query; all LLM providers failed","api/index.py hardcodes ZAI_KEY while server.py uses environment variables","Unset OPENCODE_KEY/OPENROUTER_KEY causes those providers to be skipped","Turn 2 tests: ZAI limit exceeded (resets 7/8), OpenCode key missing, Nous stepfun returns null content + reasoning only, Nous openai/nex models 404, OpenRouter key missing","Applied fix: api/index.py:chat_from_nous() reasoning fallback added","Pending: server.py needs same reasoning fix plus duplicate OpenCode call removal in call_llm"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tei0g_9a15f6f341fc","importance":6,"narrative":"Session notes document the diagnosis of failing LLM provider integrations through direct API testing. Multiple providers failed due to limit exhaustion, missing keys, null content responses, or 404 errors. Code modifications added reasoning fallbacks in chat_from_nous(), with additional server.py fixes still required.","sessi